# 17. Telegram Journal Architecture

```text
                Official Sources
                       │
                       ▼
                    Parser
                       │
                       ▼
              Normalized Dataset
                       │
                       ▼
              Publication Engine
                       │
             Canonical Rendering
                       │
                       ▼
               Telegram Journal
                       │
        ┌──────────────┼──────────────┐
        │              │              │
        ▼              ▼              ▼
 Today's Package   Tomorrow Package   Manual Posts
        │              │              │
 Updated on        Deleted next       Never touched
 Dataset change        day            by Publisher
```

